survey_response.review_text: I'm from Melbourne Australia and I visited Mumbai for the past few weeks to explore & determine which dental clinic can provide my mother with the most professional treatment for an All on Four Dental implants. From the moment I entered the Aesthetic Smile Dental Clinic I was introduced to Dr Ritika Arora. My 1st impression was the cleanliness and the fitoutis modern with the latest technology & dental equipment. Her professional approach together with her overwhelming credentials made me feel at ease immediately. She explained the complete process from start to finish from the moment you arrive in India till the day you depart. She will then sit down and explain the complete treatment plan and the costs involved so that there are no hidden surprises. Not many clinics have this credential. My mother will get her treatment  in August and I have no hesitation that this will be a great success. If you are considering dental treatment abroad then this clinic has to on top of your priority list. You may be surprised how affordable it is.

survey_response.review_text:
So with a broken bridge not sure what to do as my previous dentist had shifted base to another city . so google comes to your rescue as usual and was looking for good dental clinic. Came across Aesthetic Dental Clinic, a quick appointment, limited wait and Detailed analysis by Dr. Ritika Arora , who actually matched reviews on google , was very professional at her work and suggested me for implants . 
So I had three extracts and 3 dental implants on the same day sounds scary but the procedure was painless though some discomforts for few days but that’s a natural. After 4 months the implants were restored with 4 ceramic crowns. And so now I can eat .
Modern clinic , very professional , affordable and the overall experience at Aesthetic smiles dental clinic is good especially for nervous patients like me who tend to neglect dental treatment 
Highly recommended
